txt.en: A notice is pinned to the board:\n\n'Many unclaimed treasures are still to be found in Dor Amarth, A brave adventurer is needed to recover the treasures.'
Many unclaimed treasures await those who dare brave the realm of Dor Amarth.
Many lesser artifacts can be found scattered across Dor Amarth.\n\nYou should find any lesser artifacts that you can.
You have found many more treasures in Dor Amarth. Those you have allied with are grateful for your efforts.
